{"tid":647473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[主場讓球半] 報道:習近平將接見美方貿易團 中方或作讓步","createTime":"2018-04-30T00:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T23:45:08.000Z","uid":141151,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"3191ba2c2afc7bf8959d229fee326c969267af11","tid":647473,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:48:03.000Z","msg":"報道:習近平將接見美方貿易團 中方或作讓步<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/1831594/%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%3A%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A5%E8%A6%8B%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%B9%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%9C%98+%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E6%88%96%E4%BD%9C%E8%AE%93%E6%AD%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1831594%2F%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593%253A%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258E%25A5%25E8%25A6%258B%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%259C%2598%2B%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2588%2596%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%25AD%25A5&d=iasvbpCkUkVJl2lTLqQ2pLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7c48bb6c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/international/article/1831594/%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93%3A%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A5%E8%A6%8B%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%B9%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%9C%98+%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B9%E6%88%96%E4%BD%9C%E8%AE%93%E6%AD%A5</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n《華爾街日報》報道，中國將以高規格接待周四開始訪華的美國貿易代表團，國家主席習近平將親自接見美方官員，北京亦有意承諾削減關稅，以及放寬貿易規例，甚至作出更多友善行動，最終尋求化解兩國的貿易爭端。</span><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普本周將派出代表團訪問中國，商討中美貿易關係，代表團成員包括財長努欽、貿易代表萊特海澤、白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅、國家經濟顧問委員會總監庫德洛等，預期周四抵達北京。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">報道稱，中美兩國官員今次的會面注定是一場高風險談判。美方對中國將作出多大承諾仍抱持懷疑態度，因此計劃採取強硬立場。美方今次有違常態，在訪問北京前並無派遣先遣人員前往中國進行初步談判，而是打算在會面時，直接抛出特朗普擬徵收關稅的威脅，並向中方作出投訴，這種談判策略具相當危險性，若然成功可望推動中國深化經濟改革，但若策略不收效，或導致兩國的敵意加深。<br />\n</span><br />\n消息稱，貿易代表團為雙方緩解緊張局勢提供了機會，但快速解決問題的機會相信很渺茫。<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表辦公室依據「301調查」結果，於本月3日建議對來自中國價值約500億美元進口商品加徵25%的關稅，主要涉及訊息和通訊技術、航天航空、機械人、醫藥、機械等行業。中方認為美國的指控毫無依據。<br />\n<br />\n威脅成功會深化贏国經濟改革<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n威脅失敗純粹兩國敵意加深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即係讓完球，贏国都係坐和望贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b08be5996e872e2f4f4a255eb4527924668444d","tid":647473,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T00:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8cc52e414ed9766d5556e45fe323558704b15e3","tid":647473,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d023c1430b5d14b794b4b3c512921d0c49481b","tid":647473,"uid":53498,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:08:11.000Z","msg":"支那淆底,或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"11451f65d212aa841ab6e15ca24a907a863a4167","tid":647473,"uid":35814,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:10:37.000Z","msg":"真心口講無憑<br />\n簽完約都可以反口嘅國家<br />\n你信佢一成真係鳩都變形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de2e37e861cf3c80fe7057eb09d4a6123562678","tid":647473,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:20:56.000Z","msg":"轉個頭中國人吞埋你間公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a90596c5670655d3c69a78055825b28f8401b4","tid":647473,"uid":27882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T01:21:41.000Z","msg":"堂堂一國之君要親自招待邪惡美帝貿易團<img src=\"/assets/